INNOVATION AT THE PACE OF LIFE
We are the world’s leading global manufacturer of home appliances with $21 billion of 2016 sales while operating in nearly every country around the world. Focusing on consumer needs fuels our growth and keeps us relevant in homes around the world. We exist to create purposeful innovation that helps keep homes running smoothly so personal and family lives can flourish.

