Cooking


When game time cuts into mealtime


Skip preheating with Frozen Bake™ technology. Whirlpool® ranges let you make a meal and still get to the game right on 
time.














































































Shop Cooking




























Dishwashers


More room to load for quicker cleanup


Over 35% more rack space¹ lets you load more dishes at once. A third level rack makes sure hard-to-fit items don’t get left for later.














































































Shop Dishwashers











































































































































































































































