Washer and Dryers




 Previous Page
		        






































Laundry Appliances
Technology to keep up with any lifestyle




























Front load





Top load





Combos





Pedestals











Front load





Top load





Combos





Pedestals















Load & Go™bulk dispenser


Running late but need to keep laundry moving?


The dispenser holds enough detergent to wash up to 12 loads of laundry1 so you can simply fill it and forget it.






Shop Featured Model






Shop All Washers
























































See how much detergent the dispenser holds.










































































Learn more about the technology used to wash and dry overnight.










Wash & Dry cycle


Ready for tomorrow’s big game?


Wash and dry tomorrow’s outfit in the washer.2 This cycle uses FanFresh® technology so you don’t have to use the dryer.






Shop Featured Model






Shop All Washers




















Advanced Moisture Sensing


Need help keeping jeans from overdrying?


Sensors track moisture and temperature and adapt drying times so the cycle ends when it should. 






Shop Featured Model






Shop All Dryers
























































Learn how the sensors prevent damage from overdrying.


































































Pedestals


Comfort & Storage


Pedestals raise your laundry appliances to a more comfortable height. Select models also have additional storage for essentials.






Shop Pedestals













Choose Whirlpool® washers and dryers to keep your family’s clothes looking their best
Daily life can be messy when your family is always on the go. Whirlpool® laundry machines are made to keep up. Our innovative laundry features help you wash more in a single load. From soccer uniforms to kids’ favorite blankets, we’ll help to make sure whatever spots or splashes go into clothes, come out. Browse our full selection of washer and dryer options that’ll help you get laundry done faster so you can spend more time making messes instead of cleaning up after them.
	













