Create the lighting you need and enjoy powerful exhaust with Whirlpool range hoods. Not only do you get the reliability you can trust from Whirlpool, but these models also give you the option to create the right type of lighting to add a stylish look to your kitchen.Stylish AppearanceWhirlpool range hoods provide the powerful exhaust fans you need, and some models add a touch of beauty to your kitchen. With elegant glass-edge styles and finishes ranging from bisque to stainless steel, Whirlpool range hoods match your appliances and look great in the kitchen. If you ever need range hood parts or accessories to keep your Whirlpool appliance looking and performing like new, let Sears PartsDirect help you find what you need.Ample LightingWhirlpool range hoods offer more than just a light bulb and a couple of brightness settings. Choose from powerful halogen or LED lighting that floods your rangetop with light or functions as a night light. You can also select models featuring energy-efficient compact fluorescent lighting or the familiar glow of incandescent bulbs.Quiet and Easy to MaintainWhirlpool's newest range hood models feature insulation that keeps the noise level down even when the exhaust fans are switched to the highest speed. Some models feature hidden vents that make the hood easier to clean.Whirlpool range hoods are designed for easy installation and maintenance. If you need additional parts for your appliance, let Sears PartsDirect help. Trained technicians help you find the right parts for your range hood, and they can walk you through troubleshooting and repairs. Simply choose your model from the list above, click the chat button, or call 1-800-252-1698.




